items.headline: Welcome to the Rogue Galaxy Wiki
items.desc: Rogue Galaxy is a role playing game by Level 5, published by Sony Computer Entertainment in 2007.  It tells of the adventures of Jaster Rogue, who leaves his home planet of Rosa and joins the pirate ship Dorgenark.  The wiki covers the characters, planets, stories and more.  All are welcome to read and contribute!
